Text: Hey its always worth while d/l from Bone, hes the man, always checks and doesnt put up crap he wont watch himself! Might just be the first ones out but hey if its good for Bone its prob the best out to date so dont grumble and check it out first! :)

The imagine release has a res of 720x416 @ 25 FPS whereas this has a res of 720x404 @ 29-ish FPS hence the larger file size.. the audio on both is at 44.1Khz This release has a slight yellow tinge to the video whereas imagine is more of a pink.. its personal preference as to what you want...
